  "prompt": "Is the Indian Army well equipped?",
  "response": "The Indian Army is one of the largest and most well-equipped military forces in the world. It has a wide range of modern equipment, including advanced tanks, artillery, missile systems, and aircraft. The army continuously upgrades its capabilities through procurement and indigenous development. However, like any large military organization, there are areas where equipment and modernization efforts could be further improved. Overall, the Indian Army is considered well-equipped to handle its operational requirements.",
